import pyautogui
import time
import uiautomation as auto

try:
    auto.uiautomation.SetGlobalSearchTimeout(10)
    desktop = auto.GetRootControl()
    # Try to find and activate WhatsApp window
    whatsapp = None
    for window in desktop.GetChildren():
        if "WhatsApp" in window.Name and window.ControlType == auto.ControlType.WindowControl:
            whatsapp = window
            break
    if whatsapp:
        if not whatsapp.IsTopmost():
            whatsapp.SetTopmost(True)
        whatsapp.SetFocus()
    else:
        # Launch via Start menu
        pyautogui.hotkey('win')
        time.sleep(0.5)
        pyautogui.typewrite('WhatsApp', interval=0.05)
        time.sleep(0.5)
        pyautogui.press('enter')
        time.sleep(3)
    print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
except Exception as e:
    print(f"FAILED: {e}")
